        "Certificates of Practical Completion;",
        "full set of progress photographs as well as a documentary (to National Geographic Standard) recording the Construction Works for the period of construction and O&M Activities for at least one year of operation period including all issues of the relevant photographs recording important operations;",
        "engineering reports (such as load rating, foundation construction information, pile records, drill shafts records, etc.);",
