        "Custody Arrangements for the Base Case Financial Model",
        "The Project Company shall, no later than ten Business Days after the Execution Date, deliver two electronic copies on CD-ROM in the latest version of Microsoft Excel (or any media/software that replaces this) of the Base Case Financial Model to GOU (for GOU to hold on its own behalf).",
        "The Project Company shall submit to GOU one electronic copy on CD-ROM in the latest version of Microsoft Excel (or any media/software that replaces this) of each Base Case Financial Model (in each case becoming the Base Case Financial Model for the purposes of this Agreement) as may be revised from time to time pursuant to this section 8 of this Part A of this schedule 2.",
