        "\"Units of Measurement\" mean, for each Key Performance Indicator, the components against which the service default points for an event of non-compliance with the Key Performance Indicator shall be measured and calculated as per section 6.3 of this Part B to this schedule 2, expressed in applicable units as the case may be and as set out in each Key Performance Indicator in this schedule.",
