        "\"Lenders Step-In Period\" means the period commencing on the date of receipt by the Lenders (or the Security Trustee on their behalf) of notification by the Construction Contractor (under the Construction Consent Deed) that it has become entitled to terminate the Construction Contract in accordance with the terms of the Construction Consent Deed (a copy of which notice shall be sent simultaneously by the Construction Contractor to GOU) and ending on the earlier of:",
