        "circumstances or events which have arisen giving the Construction Contractor the right (but not the obligation) to terminate the Construction Contract and that such right of termination does not give rise to a step-in right for the Lenders (or the Security Trustee on their behalf) pursuant to the Construction Consent Deed.",
        "Interpretation",
        "In this Agreement (unless the context indicates a contrary intention):",
        "headings (including any heading at the beginning of any clause) are for convenience only and do not affect interpretation;",
        "an obligation or a liability assumed by, or a right conferred on, two or more persons binds or benefits them jointly and severally;",
