        "GOU's rights under this Agreement may not be assigned provided always that in the event that GOU assigns or transfers its rights and obligations under the Project Agreement to an assignee permitted under the Project Agreement, GOU shall be entitled to assign or transfer its rights and obligations under this Agreement to such permitted assignee.",
        "None of the Construction Contractor, the Project Company or the Construction Guarantor shall assign any of their rights under this Agreement.",
        "General Covenants and Acknowledgements",
        "Each Party represents and warrants to each other Party that:",
        "it has power to enter into this Agreement and perform its obligations under or as contemplated by this Agreement and all necessary action has been taken to authorise its execution, delivery and performance;",
        "this Agreement constitutes its valid and binding obligations enforceable against it in accordance with its terms, subject to applicable bankruptcy, reorganisation, insolvency, moratorium or similar laws affecting creditors' rights generally and subject to the availability of equitable remedies; and",
