        "Notwithstanding any provision of the Project Agreement or the Construction Contract, each of the Project Company, the Construction Contractor and the Construction Guarantor acknowledges and agrees, for the benefit of GOU:",
        "[not used]; [Note : amended as agreed in the comments matrix]",
        "to notify GOU of any event of default (or similar) by the Project Company or the Construction Contractor where such has been formally notified from one to the other under the Construction Contract, and to immediately deliver a copy of the notice of default to GOU;",
