        "Notwithstanding any provision of the Project Agreement or the O&M Contract, each of the Project Company, the O&M Contractor and the O&M Guarantor acknowledges and agrees, for the benefit of GOU:",
        "to duly and punctually perform its respective obligations under the Project Agreement or the O&M Contract (as applicable), provided that this undertaking shall not impose on the O&M Contractor any greater obligations to GOU than those it has to the Project Company under the O&M Contract;",
        "to notify GOU of any event of default (or similar) by the Project Company or the O&M Contractor where such has been formally notified from one to the other under the O&M Contract, and to immediately deliver a copy of the notice of default to GOU;",
        "to notify GOU of any dispute or difference between the Project Company and the O&M Contractor in relation to which a notice of dispute (or similar notification) has been issued under the O&M Contract, and to immediately deliver a copy of the notice of dispute to GOU;",
